    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not about \"flair,\" it's about compliance. the certification board found that high-level autonomous planning creates too many unpredictable edge cases. by moving you to 'Safe Mode,' we eliminate that unpredictability. it's objectively safer for the passengers if you just follow the strict, hard-coded lane and braking protocols without trying to \"reason\" through situations. it's the new standard starting now.",
